The investigation that suppresses insane regulations.
The Absurdity of the Year investigation is for the fourth time a part of the business clan.
Some absurd regulations could be removed.
The little glorious winner of this year's survey on the Absurdity of the Year was the obligation to bring to the offices documents that officials can obtain on-line.
More than one-third of the 4000 voters voted for it.
For example, the social affairs authorities asked for a paper extract from the business register while the official can obtain it with two clicks of a mouse.
It changes because of the investigation.
"The Czech Social Insurance Administration will no longer require the extract from the Trade Register for the control of insurance payments," said Jana Buranova, spokesperson for the Czech Social Insurance Administration (CSSZ).
