"She was at the Holesovice Exhibition Park at a party."
"What's interesting is that it didn't seem weird to the mother that her daughter was absent for 48 hours," said the Director of the Department.
It is precisely the disinterestedness of parents or their extraordinary tolerance for the fact that their offspring drink which is the main cause of the development of alcoholism among children.
According to experts, however, there is no mention of dependence, in its strict sense, on children.
"Under the term alcoholic one hears a chronic dependence on alcohol of several years with all the phenomena that follow from it but which one does not find in children".
