Morning headaches caused by dehydration and lack of glucose are eliminated by an infusion of glucose and nutrients that the body needs.
"They are better off because they spend an excellent evening then a sweet awakening and nothing hurts them".
"They are only amazed where they are," adds Pelikan, knowing that from time to time it spoils the good mood of patients at least with the note to pay for their care.
