Two L-159 aircraft are for the first time in foreign hands in Spain.
Two of the five L-159 aircraft, for which the Ministry of Defence exchanged Casa C-295M transport aircraft, took off Tuesday for Seville, Spain, where the manufacturer of Casa-EADS aircraft is based.
